          "help": "Create a new automation script. Provide content via --content or pipe from stdin. Example: cliclick scripts create my-script --content \"c:100,200 w:500 t:hello\" echo \"c:100,200\" | cliclick scripts create my-script --description \"Click test\"",
          "usage_instructions": "Create a script with --content/-c for the cliclick commands or pipe from stdin. NAME is the script name (no extension).",
          "arguments": [
            {
              "name": "name",
              "type": "TEXT",
              "required": true,
